            "answer_text": "They are basically used to restrict gallery apps from taking any media like photos,videos,etc. from the folder which has a .nomedia file. So basically any folder which has a .nomedia file, the media in those folders wont be shown in the gallery. They are mainly used to hide media which you don't want it to be shown in the gallery. ",
